<p style="text-align: center;"><em>From</em> <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781682832745" class="external" target="_blank">Daughter of a Song</a> <em>by Sarah Curtis. Copyright © 2025. Available from Texas Tech University Press.</em></p>
